title: Missouri high school football for Friday, Oct. 23, 2015
text:
Missouri high school football for Friday, Oct. 23, 2015 Featuring first-round district playoffs Helias quarterback Alex Faddoul breaks through the line of scrimmage during a game against Rock Bridge earlier this season at Adkins Stadium. Photo by Kris Wilson . Friday, October 23, 2015 
Follow our @NTsports Twitter account for gametime updates, or access the links below. When final scores come in, we'll post them on this page. Podcast episode Friday's Area District Games 
Kickoff for most district playoff games is at 7 p.m. unless otherwise noted. 
Blair Oaks hosts Versailles - Updates on Twitter: @tony_hawley . (If a live stream becomes available, we'll post the link here near gametime.) 
California hosts Southern Boone - Updates on Twitter: @CDemocratSports , @PintosAthletics and @SBooneHS . Listen live online: pintosonline.com . Watch live online: Lake TV 
Camdenton at Waynesville - Listen live online: 935rocksthelake.com 
Columbia Battle: first-round bye 
Columbia Hickman at Francis Howell - Updates on Twitter: @KewpAthletics . 
Fulton hosts Boonville - Updates on Twitter: @FultonSunSports 
Hermann hosts Principia - Updates on Twitter: @TandersonHHS 
Jefferson City hosts Columbia Rock Bridge - Updates on Twitter: @AdamBurnsJC . Listen live online: kwos.com or klik1240.com 
North Callaway hosts Van-Far - Updates on Twitter: @FultonSunSports 
Owensville hosts Eldon - Updates on Twitter: @EldonMustang , @owenathletics and @GCRepublican

Tipton at Osceola
